<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">折整求积法，方法二，求二位数乘以十几或一百零几的积，可将被乘数扩大10倍加被乘数的十位数与乘数个位之积，其和扩大10倍；再加上两个个位数相乘的积。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">35×107=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 35×107</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(35×10+3×7)×10+5×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=371×10+35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3710+35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3745</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>